style=3D'font-size:11.5pt;color:black'>&#149; Enter into an agreement to =
earn a 50%
interest in Spitzkop through Spitzkop Platinum, a domestic company that =
will
consolidate the interests of Elgin, Jonpol and a &#147;BEE to be named =
later.&#148;</span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal =
style=3D'text-align:justify;text-autospace:none'><span
style=3D'font-size:11.5pt;color:black'>&#149; Through =
&#147;Spitzplats&#148; pay US$2.5 million
to the seller &#151;Impala Platinum.</span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal =
style=3D'text-align:justify;text-autospace:none'><span
