incarnation of &#147;Spitzplats,&#148;
by paying the &#147;Eastplats&#148; shareholders a US$750,000 option =
fee.</span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal =
style=3D'text-align:justify;text-autospace:none'><span
style=3D'font-size:11.5pt;color:black'>&#149; Pay &#147;Implats&#148; =
US$14.6 million &#151; the
balance of the purchase price to acquire Spitzkop &#151; upon completion =
of the
acquisition of the property by &#147;Spitzplats.&#148;</span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal =
style=3D'text-align:justify;text-autospace:none'><span
style=3D'font-size:11.5pt;color:black'>&#149; Issue 75 million shares of =
Jonpol to
&#147;Eastplats.&#148; </span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal =
style=3D'text-align:justify;text-autospace:none'><span
style=3D'font-size:11.5pt;color:black'>&#149; Raise a minimum of C$25 =
million prior to
the closing of a Definitive Agreement between &#147;Implats&#148; and =
&#147;Spitzplats.&#148;</span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal =
style=3D'text-align:justify;line-height:25%;text-autospace:
none'><span =
style=3D'font-size:11.5pt;line-height:25%;color:black'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal =
style=3D'text-align:justify;text-autospace:none'><span
style=3D'font-size:11.5pt;color:black'>Once these myriad transactions =
are
completed, Elgin and Jonpol will then merge into a new company =
(&#147;Amalco&#148;) on
the basis of four Jonpol shares to one Elgin share.</span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal =
style=3D'text-align:justify;text-autospace:none'><span
style=3D'font-size:11.5pt;color:black'>Confusing? You bet. But after =
taking the
long road to get there, we have come right back to my original point. =
Elgin Resources
&#151; with Jonpol&#146;s help &#151; is about to buy 10 million ounces =
of near-production PGMs
for around US$30 million... <i>or $3.00 an ounce in the =
ground.</i></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal =
style=3D'text-align:justify;text-autospace:none'><span
style=3D'font-size:11.5pt;color:black'>At those prices, I can handle a =
little
complexity. The end result is that Elgin could easily double or triple =
in value
over the next few months, as it completes this complicated deal and =
advances
its properties. After that, there&#146;s tremendous leverage to the =
price of
platinum... and blue sky potential with exploration and potential new =
deals
from this talented and well-connected team. </span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal =
style=3D'text-align:justify;text-autospace:none'><span
style=3D'font-size:11.5pt;color:black'>I like to invest alongside smart,
successful people who are in the right place at the right time. =
That&#146;s
precisely the opportunity we have with Elgin.</span></p>

